menu "IO Expander Test"

    config RUN_IO_EXPANDER_TEST
        bool "Run IO Expander driver test (replaces main.c app_main)"
        default n
        help
            When enabled, the project registers io_expander_test.c as the
            sole SRCS and calls io_expander_test_run() from app_main instead
            of the original cellular_modem_basic flow.

            Use this to isolate-test the IO Expander driver before
            integrating it back into the full application.

endmenu